Hey Jared -
I know the easy thing for you to do

and take the money. That's what most
people would do. I'm just not sure that's
the right thing.

to Monica. And I'm sure you know all

anything wrong. They can be as
unreasonable as they want. I just hope
you'll rise above that.

prevail in this lawsuit. And that will likely
be a nine figure win for you. But at what
cost? Do you think you'll feel good
about that?
